Detailed Description

cvmx_bgx::_gmp_pcs_mr::_status

Bits <15:9> in this register indicate the ability to operate when BGX()_GMP_PCS_MISC()_CTL[MAC_PHY] is set to MAC mode. Bits <15:9> are always read as 0, indicating that the chip cannot operate in the corresponding modes. The field [RM_FLT] is a 'don't care' when the selected mode is SGMII.
